OL,3,CHealth board escalated to one level
OL,4,Cbelow special measures
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government has escalated
OL,7,Fintervention at Aneurin Bevan
OL,8,FUniversity Health Board (ABUHB) to one
OL,9,Fstep short of special measures.
OL,11,FJeremy Miles, Wales' health secretary,
OL,12,Fannounced the Gwent health board will
OL,13,Fmove to level four for finance and
OL,14,Femergency care on the government's
OL,15,Ffive-point scale amid concerns about
OL,16,Fan #18m financial deficit and A&E
OL,17,Ffailures.
