OL,3,CHealth board escalated to one level
OL,4,Cbelow special measures
OL,6,FIn an update to the Senedd about each
OL,7,FNHS organisation in Wales, Mr Miles
OL,8,Fsaid the health board had been at
OL,9,Flevel three due to concerns about
OL,10,Femergency care at the Grange Hospital
OL,11,Fin Cwmbran but will move to level four.
OL,13,FHe added that the health board's
OL,14,Ffinancial position has "deteriorated
OL,15,Frapidly" over the past year.
OL,17,F"It is forecasting an #18.3m deficit
OL,18,Fby the end of March. This is not
OL,19,Facceptable," he said, announcing he
OL,20,Fwill also revoke approval of the
OL,21,Fhealth board's three-year plan.
