OL,3,CHealth board escalated to one level
OL,4,Cbelow special measures
OL,6,FHe said that the health board had
OL,7,F"failed to deliver the required
OL,8,Fimprovements" since its last update
OL,9,Fand the Welsh Government escalation
OL,10,Fwas essential to "improve the
OL,11,Ftimeliness and quality of urgent and
OL,12,Femergency care for people living in
OL,13,Fthe Gwent region".
OL,15,FMr Miles announced Betsi Cadwaladr
OL,16,Fhealth board would remain at level
OL,17,Ffive or special measures. He pointed
OL,18,Fto interventions including a review of
OL,19,Fplanned care, cancer and emergency
OL,20,Fservices as well as an investigation
OL,21,Finto management of waiting times data.
