OL,6,FBut he raised to "considerable"
OL,7,Fprogress on governance and leadership
OL,8,Fat Hywel Dda health board following
OL,9,Fthe appointment of a new chair and
OL,10,Fchief executive.
OL,12,FHe announced Hywel Dda will be de-
OL,13,Fescalated to routine, level-one
OL,14,Farrangements for governance and
OL,15,Fleadership. However, the west-Wales
OL,16,Fhealth board remains at level three
OL,17,Ffor planned care and cancer as well as
OL,18,Flevel four for finance and A&E
OL,19,Fperformance.
