OL,6,FHe told Senedd members he was
OL,7,Fappointing a "senior turnaround
OL,8,Fdirector" to provide support to
OL,9,FCardiff and Vale health board, which
OL,10,Fwas placed into level four in July.
OL,12,FMr Miles said the escalation levels of
OL,13,FCwm Taf Morgannwg, Swansea Bay and
OL,14,FPowys health boards, as well as other
OL,15,FNHS bodies such as the ambulance
OL,16,Fservices trust, will not change.
OL,18,FAll seven health boards in Wales
OL,19,Fremain in some form of escalated
OL,20,Fstatus.
