OL,6,FIn today's (December 16) statement, Mr
OL,7,FMiles said long waits are falling as
OL,8,Fhe pointed to a 43% reduction in lost
OL,9,Fambulance hours since the last six-
OL,10,Fmonthly update in July.
OL,12,FHe also added that the NHS has
OL,13,Fdelivered 77,000 extra outpatient
OL,14,Fappointments to tackle the waiting
OL,15,Flist backlog.
OL,17,FBut James Evans, the Conservatives'
OL,18,Fshadow health secretary, questioned
OL,19,Fwhether intervention is delivering
OL,20,Fmeaningful improvements for patients
OL,21,Fand staff.
