OL,6,FPointing out that Betsi Cadwaladr
OL,7,Fhealth board has been "trapped" in
OL,8,Fspecial measures for most of the past
OL,9,Fdecade, he told the Senedd: "It is
OL,10,Fdeeply concerning that, once again, we
OL,11,Fsee multiple health boards at levels
OL,12,Ffour and five."
OL,14,FMr Evans urged ministers to publish
OL,15,Fperformance metrics, risk assessments
OL,16,Fand evidence used to assign escalation
OL,17,Flevels to enable decisions to be
OL,18,Fproperly scrutinised.
